<L>Why what's all this?</L>
<L>Squire Booze and his Lady.</L>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Wheat. &s;peaks</SPEAKER>
<L>Hey day, hey day!</L>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Din.</SPEAKER>
